about what I said.

550
00:27:31,698 --> 00:27:34,631
No, don't be sorry.
I am...

551
00:27:34,633 --> 00:27:36,266
I'm glad you brought it up.

552
00:27:37,702 --> 00:27:40,570
You're right.
Tim is repressed.

553
00:27:40,572 --> 00:27:43,573
