but you did say...

707
00:36:56,370 --> 00:36:57,536
How much?

708
00:37:00,707 --> 00:37:02,541
We shall hang
a plaque in your honor.

709
00:37:02,543 --> 00:37:04,576
Don't worry about it,
Carl, it's fine.

710
00:37:07,113 --> 00:37:09,448
